WEBVTT

1
00:00:05.666 --> 00:00:06.966
Stop drinking who?

2
00:00:06.966 --> 00:00:08.366
Why are you stealing my wine?

3
00:00:09.133 --> 00:00:10.300
Is that you?

4
00:00:11.066 --> 00:00:13.300
What's troubling you?

5
00:00:13.300 --> 00:00:15.500
