6
00:00:15.733 --> 00:00:16.800
Don't give me a drink

7
00:00:18.866 --> 00:00:19.700
Cheers.

8
00:00:28.266 --> 00:00:29.633
Let me tell you something.

9
00:00:30.166 --> 00:00:32.966
Men don't have a good thing

10
00:00:55.300 --> 00:00:56.633
And you know what?

11
00:00:56.966 --> 00:00:59.633
Xu Zeyu wants to divorce me

12
00:01:00.066 --> 00:01:02.833
I didn't think he would actually divorce me

13
00:01:04.400 --> 00:01:06.800
When we were together

14
00:01:07.300 --> 00:01:08.766
I'm not happy.

15
00:01:09.600 --> 00:01:11.700
He will make me happy

16
00:01:12.100 --> 00:01:13.433
Welcome with a smile

17
00:01:14.800 --> 00:01:16.066
But

18
00:01:17.200 --> 00:01:19.500
When you broke up with me this time

19
00:01:20.200 --> 00:01:22.066
He said I was strong

20
00:01:22.800 --> 00:01:25.000
Am I really that strong?

21
00:01:31.533 --> 00:01:34.100
You are fine, don't worry about his judgment

22
00:01:34.466 --> 00:01:36.166
I will always be by your side

23
00:01:38.566 --> 00:01:39.400
fool

24
00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:42.566
